ation\">(</span>source<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"source\"><code>source</code></dt>\n <dd>一个 <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>BufferSource</code></a> 对象（<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypedArray\"><code>ArrayBufferView</code></a> 或&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer</code></a>），存储了你要添加到 SourceBuffer 中去的媒体片段数据。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"Return value","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>undefined</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exceptions","title":"Exceptions","isH3":true,"content":"<p>None.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":"<p>TBD.</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-appendbuffer","title":"Media Source Extensions™"}],"query":"api.SourceBuffer.appendBuffer"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.SourceBuffer.appendBuffer","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/SourceBuffer/appendBuffer/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect5\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaSource\"><code>MediaSource</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SourceBufferList\"><code>SourceBufferList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syn